ABOUT pkgmk


  This directory contains pkgmk, a package management utility, which
  makes a software package.

  It is a fork of CRUX' pkgmk (extracted from pkgutils source).  It
  was rewritten in POSIX shell, added support of aria2 downloader,
  and adjusted for zeppe-lin distribution.

  The original sources can be downloaded from:

    1. https://crux.nu/gitweb/?p=tools/pkgutils.git;a=summary
    2. git://crux.nu/tools/pkgutils.git


  DEPENDENCIES

    Built time:

    * make(1p)
    * pod2man(1pm)

    For downloading the distfiles pkgmk needs one of the following:

    * aria2
    * curl
    * wget (is used by default)

    Runtime:

    * sh(1)
    * bsdtar(1)

    And in any case:

    * POSIX utilities


